						<summary>

						<p>Stone near the Pōlēramma temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1441, Pramādi, Kārttika śu. 15, Sunday, lunar eclipse</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1517 A.D., November 6, Sunday, lunar eclipse.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record a gift of land as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> at Gundlapalli by Koṇēnri Yaṟaya.</p>						

						</summary>
